name: Soileire Business Solutions
overview:
Soileire Business Solutions is a sourcing and import company specialising in trade between China and Ireland.

Having worked with Chinese companies over the past 15 years, the founder Sean Hennessy set up his own business, serving Irish customers who want to initiate imports from China. Soileire works closely with Chinese company Asiaway Trading, which is based in Shenzhen, China. It is owned and operated by and Irish citizen. Asiaway acts as Soileire’s eyes and ears on the ground in China.

Sean has experience of importing a wide variety of commodities, and together with Aisaway, offers Irish Clients a full turnkey service including sourcing, supplier audit, price negoitiation, quality inspection, shipping customs clearance and local delivery in Ireland.
